{"tid":1196719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥:若違主流意見會辭職","createTime":"2019-06-09T22:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T23:18:39.000Z","uid":156363,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5c29d20b3e81b0f41d80357f732c9a4ea7b82d","tid":1196719,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:59:51.000Z","msg":"行政長官候選人林鄭月娥於選舉論壇中突爆出「辭職論」，稱如果港人主流意見認為她不適合擔任特首，就會辭職。曾俊華質疑對方未上任民望已見負數，應考慮退選，又諷刺林鄭於facebook「嬲嬲已經去到個鼻」。對於林鄭公開「挖角」其助理羅永聰，曾回應說團隊「錢買唔到」。<br />\n<br />\n曾諷林鄭負民望 「會唔會考慮退選？」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　林鄭月娥被觀眾問及，如果她的立場與社會主流意見不同時會如何處理，林鄭回應說百分百相信香港人，某些事件上若主流意見與她的不同，她會接受港人意見，「如果港人主流意見認為我不適合再擔任特首，我會辭職」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　曾俊華於最後環節自由時段向林鄭發炮，引述嶺南大學民意調查指，林鄭支持度僅30%，反對比例卻高達45%，未上任已經「負淨值」，「會唔會考慮退選？」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　林鄭回應稱，不同調查有不同問法，「有一個，我支持度高過你3個百分點。」曾俊華馬上指「你信嗰個？」林鄭引述的調查是由有建制背景的香港研究協會進行。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　林鄭又說，「民望可上可落，好多人選的時候民望好高，之後跌得好快」。曾俊華隨即嘲諷「你講邊個？」林鄭便回應，「好多外國總統都係咁」。"},{"pid":"3426b550f48f58756af67917a8fc299525455cb5","tid":1196719,"uid":25601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/10/070103_85bb24e9566a486c06c56a32114f6488.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F070103_85bb24e9566a486c06c56a32114f6488.png&h=f67c1364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/10/070117_0ea57e2065058eae785af822c5893541.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F070117_0ea57e2065058eae785af822c5893541.png&h=e0cb3618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/10/070129_4228897f430b8a252b40913126c82b65.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F070129_4228897f430b8a252b40913126c82b65.jpeg&h=31bf8476&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e8e8a50e4713a99bd78f99d7bcdce1db99ae90b","tid":1196719,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/10/070124_b96a65ee3c24569834caaa61d2c58a74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F070124_b96a65ee3c24569834caaa61d2c58a74.jpg&h=feab95e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾俊華又諷刺林鄭不受網民歡迎，「你有冇睇facebook live？你塊面下面啲嬲嬲已經去到你個鼻度。」林鄭指自己在網上是弱者，反指對方在政府工作仍有很多時間在網上「儲like」，曾稱「其實唔用幾多時間」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　林鄭又指，曾俊華擅於利用社交媒體，只因有前政治助理羅永聰幫忙，更指如果自己當選，會考慮聘請羅永聰。曾俊華說自己的團隊「係錢買唔到嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　林鄭又稱，為政府節省金錢，她沒有聘請政治助理。翻查資料，林鄭上任時曾聘用政治助理張秀麗，張不足一年後辭職。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　特首候選人共三人，包括曾俊華、林鄭月娥及胡國興。"},{"pid":"c15293b1fd1cb0a11c4f4460cda970e155e545e1","tid":1196719,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f0af05c58d9069daad36c8f3d4b979598da148","tid":1196719,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:03:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無恥至極</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n或者叫 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">厚顏無恥</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1b68c49f5bcdb6cb3cb8d3d96b452cf31d5e4bc7","tid":1196719,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:04:05.000Z","msg":"屌那星，仲開心咗幾秒鐘"},{"pid":"711e82e38f59c9ccca83ae4abb17d9de70fa4a18","tid":1196719,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:06:54.000Z","msg":"又post返呢啲出黎有咩意思 同大台叫口號自high有咩分別"},{"pid":"93597d03de761a8b610be2ffeb052c6d92e3719f","tid":1196719,"uid":174775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:08:17.000Z","msg":"俾呢D女人管香港，真係笑話"},{"pid":"030bbd61e261beeed2e023c6a6f222416c74a200","tid":1196719,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ed1092694dc6a2130b6a09877ad2701ad63bee","tid":1196719,"uid":26675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T23:18:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 仲拎依句打飛機<br />\n醒未阿渠頭"}]}